{"tid":859763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「收皮啦」香港變蝗啦撚屌們 行動證明一切啊！","createTime":"2018-10-12T18:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T19:00:27.000Z","uid":204565,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b26586f8eeab7c5cad60211235c3eba61cceee98","tid":859763,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港豬真係好撚戇鳩啊！！！</span></span><br />\n每一次見撚到個狗府有問題淨係識用把口去屌<br />\n但係又唔撚行動去解決個問題<br />\n日日淨係識屌鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同啲尻閪老屎忽有乜撚野分別啊！！！</span></span><br />\n港豬係時候做下野啦！<br />\n個個都好撚似等比人屠宰既豬一撚樣！！<br />\n港豬唔係冇能力啊！只係個撚個都坐以待斃啊！<br />\n<br />\n冇撚用架屌！！人人都等有人企出黎帶頭，個撚個都怕做第一個比人收皮先，鬼唔撚知槍會打出頭鳥咩！但冇人肯行第一步又邊撚到有人肯跟肯理啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做野啦港豬！情願得過且過定係盡力搏多次啊！成日係到話搏盡無悔，係唔撚搏盡啊?企出黎啦屌你老母！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個政府做啲閪野做撚到咁撚樣仲等?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論邊個睇到都好我都想你班撚屌企出黎！<br />\n做一樣你人生最值得做既野！企出黎屌撚爆個垃圾政府！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我推撚爆佢比所有港豬撚屌都睇撚到<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fcf2467a3e1c7542937f383dc0832687aa2ee44a","tid":859763,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"推啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b29159170d892e78729c5ce5f3136946d3b56fa","tid":859763,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,